name: Schematics & Manuals
tagline: A repository to collect information and schematics, manuals, and perhaps other ephemera for music equipment and electronics.
body:
### Welcome to Schematics & Manuals.
This is a work in progress collection of schematics, manuals, and other ephemera related to music equipment and/or electronics. If you have any documents to contribute, please don't hesitate to do so!
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
